ygData.messageBody:
Just a quick note on your revenge list of
Fippy
Fippy
Fippy
i hope you are aware that there is a FLIPPY Darkpaw and a Fippy Darkpaw.
the first being the infamous newbie killer in qeynos whom i kill everytime i
go back there...(i am lvl 24 warrior now) <grin>
and the second being a GM of verant who spawns himself up top of
blackburrow. Fippy is lvl 17, and if u catch him in a good mood and hail him
speaking Gnoll he will actually talk to...
i was told this by a apprentice gm one day and i didn't believe him... so i
went and waited in BB after paying 5pp to learn Gnoll..
1day went by and no Fippy
2day and no Fippy
and on the 3rd day i just happened to be at the right place and the right
time...FIPPY SPAWNED. then after a short conversation he proceeded to kick
my butt...
Moral of the Story
I have no clue but it was neat talking to him..
